==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Forfend
<hw>For*fend"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>for-</ets> + <ets>fend</ets>. See <er>Forewend</er>.]</ety> <def>To
prohibit; to forbid; to avert.</def> <mark>[Archaic]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Which peril heaven <qex>forefend</qex>!</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><note>⟦hand⟧ This is etymologically the preferable
spelling.</note>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Forfered</ent>⟦br⟧
